title: Moreana
additional-note: This is a European publication. Its contents may still be copyrighted even without renewals or copyright notices, if they meet GATT copyright restoration requirements for works first published outside the US. Some issues mention US subscription rates and a US address for an affiliated organization. Spot-checks of issues from the mid-1980s did not turn up copyright notices.
acknowledgement: Thanks to Shelton Henderson for copyright research on this title.
